 accuracy as the RGB model. Ultimately, the choice between the RGB and HSB color models depends on the specific needs of the application or project, and what kind of visual effect is desired. Regardless of whether you use the RGB or HSB color model, however, there are always several ways to manipulate and interpret the colors that result from
